::Hot Rod::

Hot Rod walked out to Kamodia. 
"Sorry we were rude. We have to wait for Iron Rapter to give us the ok."
He siad. He then walked into his room, and went to sleep.

::DrillBit:: 

DrillBit was tired from the battles, so he went to his room, and went to
sleep.

::K-9::

"I should go hide by ship." He says, walking to his ship. He started her
up, and piloted her to a hidden place. When he got there, he landed the
ship, cloacked her, and went to sleep.
